		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I was going through older posts and I just wanted to say I think you should develop the Vigilante game, it's quite nice!<br /><br />If it had more detailed animation/bg etc I think it would be a really great experience. There are some internal tweaks you could make, for example when you hold down the punch or jump button the character continually jumps or punches. <br /><br />I'm not sure how exactly it works on NES, but you should check the the user input in a way where you check for the buttons being pressed and see if they are different than the previous frame, this way you can see whether the button was pressed or held.

		

		</td>
