		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I tried Vigilante right now. It's pretty cool, congratulations!<br />The only problem is: the floor will not appear on NTSC televisions.<br />Seems that your game was designed to use NES' full resolution (256 x 240) but people who plays at 256 x 224 won't be able to see the entire stage.<br /><br /><a href="http://s5.photobucket.com/user/macbee/media/prpl_zpsucbpl6ei.png.html" class="postlink"><img src="http://i5.photobucket.com/albums/y191/macbee/th_prpl_zpsucbpl6ei.png" alt="Image" /></a>

		

